{
  "stem": "10283.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had coffee somewhere, or were sitting somewhere, and we met.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's where our courtship started again, you know, in the springtime.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And everything was very romantic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, he was not so romantic.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He had frozen ears from being in the hiding in France.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he had frozen [? hand ?] fingers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And his teeth were bad, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was also in [INAUDIBLE] for these two years.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But he was young, and, you now, most young people survived much better, and endured much better, and were more optimistic, or more energetic.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so we started our friendship.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then one day, I-- we were in that camp, in-- in Bienenberg, it was called.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's still there, I hear.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It's a hotel near-- between Basel and Liestal, up on the hill [? light. ?]",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, that was Bienenberg.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We got out of Buren and got to this-- this camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was an old hotel.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were housed in-- in regular rooms, mostly three in a room, too.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My mother and I.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was another young lady was with us in this room.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that was already better.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were out of the weather.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we-- we had the bathroom on the floor, at least.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we had a dining room, and the food wasn't great.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But we were never hungry, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they made-- the men had, really, harder work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But in his camp, in the men's camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we were mostly doing make work, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had-- they cut strips of fabric.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And were weaving those rags that you-- they still do.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and of course, they had to work in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Some worked in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Some working in the cleaning.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And some worked in the laundry.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I had already started my apprenticeship as-- as a dressmaker.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So there was a dressmaker, and from a Viennese Viennese dressmaker in this camp, also.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And there came boxes of donated clothing that people had donated to the refugees.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they had to be altered because they didn't always fit.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I told her I can sew, and I can do a little bit.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I worked with her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I learned how to do alterations and how to-- you know, I learned that later on, they had-- they emptied a big room.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they had babies in there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They have refugee babies that are there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But they didn't want each mother to take care of its baby.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They wanted to streamline that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So there was a trained baby nurse from France.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And she requested that I help with her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So I did this, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But people, they were occupied.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Everybody had some kind of an occupation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, very minimum, maybe.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But then we had-- later, we had every six weeks, the railroad gave us a 100-mile radius, free transportation.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And every six weeks, we could go for two or three days on-- on furlough.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because the families were mostly separated, the husbands and wives.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The men were in one camp, and the wives were in the other.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So in order to facilitate this-- well, I didn't have a husband.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And neither did my mother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I went with Werner a few times.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were in Basel, and we were in-- in-- in the winter we went to Basel.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And in the summer, we went on lakes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And so our friendship grew, and our courtship grew.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then one day, the-- the director of my camp came and said, they have a-- an enquiry for dressmaker.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For operator, we would call it here, in the blouse factory in Bern, and would I want to go to Bern and work there on a power machine?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So when Werner heard that, he put in the only way he could get out of the camp was being a dishwasher.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he-- they were short on those labor-intensive things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he put in for dishwasher, and within one week, he was in Bern, washing dishes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was still in the camp because my liberation took a little longer.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But we finally got together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he had to live on top in the-- in the attic with other dishwashers, other crooks.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was very primitive, and very amazing to us how unsanitary and primitive the conditions were in a first-class-- so-called first-class restaurant in Bern.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But he made it through.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I had that job in the blouse factory.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then we decided to get married.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And through different circumstances, too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we-- my mother gave her consent.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And on the 1st of May in 1945, we got married in Bern.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
